KYC (Know Your Customer) verification process is necessary to ensure the security and legitimacy of card usage. It is an
essential prerequisite for using the Immersve card.

Immersve provides partners with the following options for doing KYC:

- [Partner Conducted KYC](/guides/partner-conducted-kyc)
- [Immersve Conducted KYC](/guides/immersve-conducted-kyc)
